{
  "texts": [
    "We do our best to clean the article texts, and remove those with no discernible semantic information.",
    "We normalize all punctuation and remove any embedded URLs, HTML, or Markdown markup.",
    "SpaCy's (Montani et al. 2023) en_core_web_sm was used to annotate all tokens in the corpora.",
    "We identify self-references as named entities with a large longest common substring relative to the publisher's name.",
    "We also mask any sentences which SpaCy flags as being part of an email, URL or twitter handle."
  ]
}